    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really great shape for all your upcoming adventures! It runs super smoothly, looks sharp on the road, and has plenty of life left in it. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to go, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love for you to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
