      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-taken care of? This beauty is ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s in great shape and drives like a dream. I\u2019ve loved every mile in it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
