      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver-spec example boasts a factory-equipped limited-slip differential and retains its legendary 8,000 RPM redline performance. Vital preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure precise variable valve timing. The chassis remains taut with upgraded poly-bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing exceptional lateral grip and feedback. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast car, the powertrain and drivetrain synchronization are superb, offering the raw, analog feedback these M-cars are known for.",
